{
  "texts": [
    "What if we augment AuSTR with the cross-domain datasets in training?",
    "Fig. 8 illustrates that effect.",
    "For every single cross-domain dataset, when augmented with AuSTR, the resulted model outperforms the model trained only on the cross-domain data by a big margin, ranging from 6.8-35.6% in macro-F 1.",
    "This re-emphasizes the effect of in-domain data.",
    "However, only the model trained on AuSTR+AraStance was able to outperform the AuSTR-only model in macro-F 1 and F 1 (agree), but not F 1 (disagree)."
  ]
}